 4627 00		      C verify_frontend_ticks db 0
 4628 00		      C verify_frontend_event_fired db 0
 4629 FF		      C last_game_state db 0FFh
 462A 00		      C feedback_timer db 0
			      C ; The runner's last committed step lets flanking hunters aim one tile ahead
			      C ; without any hidden extra turns or non-deterministic guesses.
